By combining Givaudan’s leading product technology and application expertise with Naturex’s natural ingredients, we offer solutions to help you create food experiences your consumers will love. Built on its global leadership position in flavors and taste, the Company goes beyond to create food experiences that do good and feel good, for body, mind and planet.

data.name: StabilEnhance
data.description: Meet your consumer's expectations by using the StabilEnhance product line.  These are natural, clean label products available to support shelf life extension. Plant extracts, like rosemary, can be used to protect taste and color while providing transparency on the label. Rosemary extract can support your clean-label strategy by slowing the oxidation processes that cause off-flavors and color changes.  It is sustainably and ethically sourced.  StabileEnhance can be used in a variety of applications, such as meat & poultry, beverages, sauces/dressings, and plant-based products.  If you are looking to add more protection, check out our line of blended ingredients - Xtrablend and OxyBlock - that help protect products during different parts of the oxidation process.

data.name: LIFENOL
data.description: Lifenol is a patented plant extract obtained using hops responsibly sourced in Bavaria and extracted in our plant in Milan, whose core form of industrial expertise is the processing of botanical extracts.

data.name: TURMIPURE GOLD
data.description: TURMIPURE GOLD is world’s first bioequivalent turmeric at a low dose. Its 100% natural and organic formulation highly enhances bioavailability of curcuminoids, in addition to being instant water dispersible.

data.name: Flowens
data.description: Flowens™, a full spectrum cranberry based ingredient specifically developed for men’s health. This optimized formula is supported by gold standard clinical evidence illustrating its ability to improve Lower Urinary Tract Symptoms (LUTS) typically associated with Benign Prostatic Hyperplasia (BPH).   Over 50% of men in their fifties and 80% of men in their seventies suffer from BPH resulting in a potential market of over 26 million men in the US alone.

data.name: ACEROLIFE
data.description: Acerolife is a brand of acerola cherry fruit powders optimized to deliver high levels of naturally occurring vitamin C content. Acerolife branded ingredients have been developed using fruits harvested at the right level of maturity to optimize content of vitamin C, flavor and cost. Ingredients under this brand are sustainably sourced in Brazil under the strictest responsible sourcing standards and in close collaboration with the communities that grow and cultivate the acerola. Acerolife ingredients are ideal for use as a source of natural vitamin C in dietary supplements, beverages and foods.

data.name: PACran
data.description: Pacran® scientific validity as a natural ingredient for urinary health management has recently been recognized by the Canadian Health Authorities. With a minimum daily dose of 500 mg, all finished products using Pacran® can make claims such as “helps prevent recurrent urinary tract infections in women” or “used in Herbal Pacran® receives approved urinary tract health claims from Canadian authorities.

data.name: ARONOX
data.description: Aronox® is an extract of aronia (Aronia melanocarpa; Aronia mitschurinii) that delivers heart health benefits supported by several published peer-reviewed clinical trials, with significant improvements observed within just one month of use. Aronia, also known as chokeberry, wild gooseberry, chokepear or dogberry, is rich in polyphenols.

data.name: Naturex Elderberry Fruit Powder 4% Anthocyanins HPLC (ON700002)
data.description: Naturex Elderberry Fruit Powder 4% Anthocyanins HPLC (ON700002) is elderberry juice powder made from the fruit of Sambucus nigra L. It appears as a dark red-purple powder and has a characteristic flavor. The composition includes fruit solids. This product is non-GMO and water-soluble.

data.name: StabilEnhance® OSR D 4 Deodorized Rosemary (BA201290)
data.description: StabilEnhance® OSR D 4 Deodorized Rosemary (BA201290) is a liquid product with a neutral sensory profile. It is derived from rosemary leaves using acetone as the extraction solvent. The composition includes sunflower oil and rosemary extract. This product is certified as kosher parve and halal.

data.name: Naturex CHIPOTLE PEPPER SAUCE CONCENTRATE (NV01SB54)
data.description: Naturex CHIPOTLE PEPPER SAUCE CONCENTRATE (NV01SB54) is produced using fresh, fully ripened red jalapeño peppers. The peppers undergo a meticulous process that includes washing and de-stemming, followed by natural wood smoking to impart a distinctively smoky and spicy pepper flavor. These smoked peppers then undergo further processing, involving acidification with vinegar and heat pasteurization, ultimately resulting in the creation of the unique Chipotle Pepper Sauce Concentrate. It's essential to note that this product is manufactured in full compliance with FDA and State of California Department of Health regulations, ensuring its quality and safety.

data.name: ACEROLIFE M 20% VITAMIN C NATURALLY OCCURING (ON700011)
data.description: ACEROLIFE M 20% VITAMIN C NATURALLY OCCURING (ON700011) is a powdered juice derived from the expression of acerola fruits. Its composition includes fruit solids and magnesium hydroxide as an acidity regulator. The product presents as a powder with an orange to orange-brown color and a characteristic odor and taste of acerola. It is water-soluble.

data.name: XtraBlend® RA Blend (BA255533)
data.description: XtraBlend® RA Blend (BA255533) is a powdered product with a neutral sensory profile, showing colors from orange to light orange. It is sourced from acerola and rosemary and created through an extraction and blending process. The extraction solvent used is a combination of water and acetone. The composition includes corn syrup solids, green acerola juice solids, rosemary extract, and sodium hydroxide. This product is certified as kosher parve and halal.

data.name: Organic StabilEnhance® WSR 5.5 Rosemary (BCN00501)
data.description: Organic StabilEnhance® WSR 5.5 Rosemary (BCN00501) is an extract obtained from organically certified rosemary leaves (Rosmarinus officinalis L.). It is a fine powder with a yellow-brown color and a light, tea-like flavor. This product is water-soluble and compliant with the US Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act.

data.name: Naturex CHIPOTLE IN ADOBO (NV01SB50)
data.description: Naturex CHIPOTLE IN ADOBO (NV01SB50) is produced using fresh, whole, fully ripened red jalapeño peppers. These peppers are meticulously washed and destemmed before being subjected to natural wood smoking, imparting a distinctive smoky, spicy flavor. The smoked peppers then undergo further processing, involving acidification with vinegar and heat pasteurization, resulting in the creation of our unique Chipotle in Adobo. It's important to note that these products adhere to strict processing standards in compliance with FDA and State of California Department of Health regulations.

data.description: Naturex POBLANO PEPPER PUREE, FIRE ROASTED, ACIDIFIED (NV00PB50) serves as a spice. It is presented in the form of a coarse puree with a dark green color that includes charred pieces of skin, and no seeds are visible. The flavor is typical of roasted poblano peppers. data.name: Anti-Blemish Cream
data.description: A cream for oily skin prone to imperfections. Reduces spots and smoothes the skin thanks to salicylic acid, which acts as an anti-bacterial and exfoliating agent. Soft and non greasy cream that regulates skin deficits in essential fatty acids, moisturizes and eliminates excess sebum.

data.name: Eutectyserum
data.description: Innovative serum formulated with Olive leaf Eutectys™ BG to promote collagen synthesis and actively fight against wrinkles and volume loss. Improves skin resistance, elasticity and suppleness. 100% natural, its unique texture is based on a new type of solvent, NaDES, recently discovered in the plant core, which is neither hydrophilic nor lipophilic. A true superserum, Eutectyserum has the same fascinating intermediate property, as it provides all the sensorial and comfortable touch of an oil…without a single drop of oil in the formula!
